data.description: Built in 2019!! This immaculate, 4 Yr. Old K.Hovnanian brick and stone 2-story, 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, has an open concept with high ceilings as soon as you enter! This home has a grand entry 8-foot front door, luxury plank vinyl flooring throughout the main entertaining areas, modern cabinets, granite countertops, great living space with a large backyard for entertaining family and friends! This home is equipped with water softener system and sprinkler system. 2.5 tandem car garage with some built in shelves, workbench, bike racks, and fishing racks for future homeowners!
